channel.title: I made a new webclient but
channel.description:
I recently made a new web client on [url=http://www.life-scape.ucoz.com]www.life-scape.ucoz.com[/url]
Unfortunately it isn't working properly. I'm not sure if my failure to sign it is what caused this, but if you know anything, please post on this topic. As you can see it keeps getting a little red X on a piece of paper in the corner, this happens on every computer. If it starts to load, it will just "pretend" like its loading for about a minute or two, then the red X on the piece of paper will appear.
All Help is appricated! :D
